titles: Pronostic merveilleux sur l'estrange maladie du sieur Dom Diego d'Aualos.
notes: A satire against Spain in the form of a dialogue in verse.
Verse - "Espagnol dont la faim n'est iamais assouuie".
Allegorical engraving of the continents and countries involved in the dialogue at head of text.
Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
